title: Microsoft Office Enterprise 2007 SP3 VL x86 en-US September 2015
description:
****************************************************************
Microsoft Office Enterprise 2007 SP3 VL x86 en-US September 2015
****************************************************************

Microsoft Office Enterprise 2007 includes: Word, Excel, PowerPoint, Access, Outlook, Publisher, InfoPath, Groove, OneNote, and Office Communicator and supports ECM, electronic forms, and IRM/RMS.

System requirements:

- OS: Windows 7, Windows Server 2003, Windows Vista, Windows XP
- Memory: 512 MB RAM

Release Info:

- Language: en-US
- Channel: Volume License
- Includes SP2, SP3 and KB files until 30 September 2015
- File: Office12-ENT-SP3-x86-en-US-Sept2015.rar (rar compressed iso image)
- Size: 1.31 GB

- CRC32: 70b78d0a
- MD4: 917240e455cd671626e1bf63800fa69d
- MD5: 5f5de1d83dcc394a19d2d192d872432e
- SHA-1: b9de3a4a05557fe9a01258de28e0f2e35f0d6e56

Installation:

- Unrar, mount or burn Office12-ENT-SP3-x86-en-US-Sept2015.iso
- Install Office 2007 using one of the provided keys in key.txt
- Install Office File Validation (mandatory security add-in for Office 2007) from folder "1. Run after install"
- Install desired Add-ins from folder "2. Add-ins"

Add-ins:

- Classic Menu for Office 2007 v7.50
- FileFormatConverters
- PowerPointViewer
- SaveAsPDFandXPS
- Wordview_en-us
